                <entry colsep="1" rowsep="1"><para role="TEXT">Business roll day
                convention for resets that fall on non-business days. See
                <emphasis>Table 4 - Business Roll Day Convention</emphasis> in
                chapter <emphasis>Tables</emphasis> for an explanation of the
                options.</para></entry>
              </row>

              <row>
                <entry colsep="1" rowsep="1"><para role="TEXT"><guilabel>Reset
